  "title": "MARKETING & SALES EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong><br /><br />We are a well-established Construction and Manpower Supply Company in Singapore seeking a motivated Marketing Executive to support business developmentand client engagement in the local market.<br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Promote construction and manpower supply services to local clients</li><li>Develop new business opportunities</li><li>Develop new clients and maintain existing relationships</li><li>Liaise with Mandarin-speaking clients and business partners</li><li>Conduct market research and prepare marketing strategies and business proposals </li><li>Conduct client meetings, site visits, and follow-ups</li><li>Achieve sales and business development targets</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Marketing, Business, or related field</li><li>Minimum<strong> </strong>3 – 5 years of relevant experience (construction/manpower industry preferred)</li><li>Proficient in English and Mandarin (to liaise with Mandarin-speaking clients)</li><li>Good communication, negotiation, presentation and interpersonal skills</li><li>Familiar with Singapore construction market and MOM regulations (advantage)</li><li>Ability to work independently and meet targets</li><li>Singapore Citizens or Permanent Residents preferred</li></ul><p><strong>Salary & Benefits</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Monthly Salary:</strong> SGD <strong>[2800 – 4500]</strong>\n     (Negotiable, based on experience)</li><li>Commission / Performance Incentives</li><li>Career progression opportunities</li></ul>",
